item.description: Our chapter has been a part of Relay for Life for a few years now. Many of our members lives have been affected and continue to be affected by Cancer. This event starts at 3p on Friday June 12th and ends at 3p on Saturday June 13th. If you are interested in being on our team-please visit http://main.acsevents... You'll need to go join an existing team, simply called South Windsor Jaycees. Please note that the chapter will pay your registration fee, so if you haven't already become a member (paid your dues), please do so before June 12th!
item.name: Relay for Life-South Windsor
